302
00:24:07,290 --> 00:24:08,290
I'm having a business dinner tonight.

303
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:10,670
There's dinner for you on the table.

304
00:24:10,670 --> 00:24:11,580
Heat it up yourself.

305
00:24:12,080 --> 00:24:14,670
