to a fancy meal tomorrow.

306
00:24:33,210 --> 00:24:34,080
[Platinum Hotel]
Come on, San Pang. Cheers!

307
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:34,920
Cheers.

308
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:36,670
